# 🎉 Kids Online Quiz Application

A fun and interactive quiz application for kids with music, videos, and images.

## 🌟 Features

- 🎨 Colorful kid-friendly UI
- 🎵 Background music
- 🎬 Educational video
- 🧠 Quiz with scoring system
- 📊 Result storage in MongoDB
- 🌐 REST API backend

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

Frontend:
- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript

Backend:
- Node.js
- Express.js
- MongoDB

## 🚀 Installation

### 1. Clone Repository
git clone https://github.com/your-username/kids-quiz-app.git

### 2. Install Backend Dependencies
cd backend
npm install

### 3. Run Server
node server.js

Server runs at:
http://localhost:5000

